<p>Network data confirm the restriction of Twitter on multiple internet providers in Turkey as of Wednesday 8 February 2023. The incident comes as authorities raise concerns over disinformation online, although no formal explanation has been provided. Service was restored the next morning after state media <a href="https://www.trthaber.co" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">reported</a> that Turkish authorities had held a meeting with Twitter’s head of policy on disinformation and the need for content takedowns.</p>
